# Problems - Mathematical Epidemiology {-}

- **Problems 1.1** Simple models and Host heterogeneity (Chs 2 & 3 of Keeling and Rohani - Greer)

- **Problems 1.2** Host heterogeneity and Multipathogen/Multihost (Chs 3 & 4 of Keeling and Rohani - Heffernan)

- **Problems 1.3** Within-host models (Heffernan)

- **Problems 1.4** Pathogen evolution and temporally-forced models (Ch 5 of Keeling and Rohani - Heffernan)

- **Problems 1.5** Stochastic dynamics and spatial models (Ch 6 & 7 of Keeling and Rohani - Arino)

- **Problems 1.6** Spatial models and importations (Ch 7 of Keeling and Rohani - Arino)

- **Problems 1.7** Zoonotic spillover (Greer)

- **Problems 1.8** Controlling infectious diseases (Ch 8 of Keeling and Rohani - Greer)